completed_orders: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, p.price FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.status = 'delivered' ORDER BY p.price DESC
expensive_electronics: SELECT name, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category IN ('Electronics', 'Appliances') AND price > 100 AND name LIKE '%e%'
02_product_summary: SELECT id, name, price AS cost, category AS type FROM ecommerce_products
03_electronics_only: SELECT name, price, brand FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category = 'Electronics'
04_expensive_items: SELECT name, price, category FROM ecommerce_products WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC
05_affordable_electronics: SELECT name, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category = 'Electronics' AND price < 50
06_furniture_or_office: SELECT name, category, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category = 'Furniture' OR category = 'Office' ORDER BY category, name
07_multiple_categories: SELECT name, category, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category IN ('Electronics', 'Appliances', 'Furniture') ORDER BY price DESC
08_exclude_stationery: SELECT name, category FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category NOT IN ('Stationery', 'Office') ORDER BY name
09_products_with_desk: SELECT name, category, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE name LIKE '%Desk%' ORDER BY price
10_no_wireless: SELECT name, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category = 'Electronics' AND name NOT LIKE '%Wireless%'
11_no_delivery_date: SELECT orderId, productId, status FROM ecommerce_orders WHERE deliveryDate IS NULL
12_delivered_orders: SELECT orderId, status, deliveryDate FROM ecommerce_orders WHERE deliveryDate IS NOT NULL ORDER BY deliveryDate
13_complex_filter: SELECT name, price, category FROM ecommerce_products WHERE (category = 'Electronics' AND price > 100) OR (category = 'Furniture' AND price < 100)
14_orders_with_products: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, p.price, o.quantity, o.status FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id
15_high_value_delivered: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, p.price, o.quantity FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.status = 'delivered' AND p.price > 100 ORDER BY p.price DESC
16_top_10_electronics: SELECT TOP 10 name, price, brand FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category = 'Electronics' ORDER BY price DESC
17_sample_mid_range: SELECT name, price, category FROM ecommerce_products WHERE price >= 20 AND price <= 100 ORDER BY price LIMIT 15
18_advanced_filter: SELECT name, price, brand FROM ecommerce_products WHERE category IN ('Electronics', 'Appliances') AND price > 50 AND name LIKE '%e%' AND brand IS NOT NULL ORDER BY price
19_active_electronics_orders: SELECT o.orderId, p.name AS product, o.status, o.orderDate FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.status IN ('shipped', 'processing') AND p.category = 'Electronics' ORDER BY o.orderDate DESC
20_not_cheap_electronics: SELECT name, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE NOT (category = 'Electronics' AND price < 30) AND category IS NOT NULL
21_out_of_stock: SELECT name, category, brand FROM ecommerce_products WHERE inStock = false OR stock = 0
22_low_stock_alert: SELECT name, stock, category FROM ecommerce_products WHERE stock > 0 AND stock < 50 ORDER BY stock
23_brands_starting_with_a: SELECT name, brand, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE brand LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY brand, price
24_cancelled_orders: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, o.orderDate, o.totalPrice FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.status = 'cancelled'
25_bulk_orders: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, o.quantity, o.totalPrice FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.quantity >= 5 ORDER BY o.quantity DESC
26_desk_or_monitor_items: SELECT name, category, price FROM ecommerce_products WHERE name LIKE '%Desk%' OR name LIKE '%Monitor%' ORDER BY name
27_complex_nested: SELECT name, price, category FROM ecommerce_products WHERE ((category = 'Electronics' AND price < 50) OR (category = 'Stationery' AND price < 20)) AND inStock = true
28_pending_deliveries: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, o.orderDate, o.status FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.deliveryDate IS NULL AND o.status != 'cancelled' ORDER BY o.orderDate
29_mid_price_range: SELECT name, category, price, brand FROM ecommerce_products WHERE price >= 50 AND price <= 150 ORDER BY category, price DESC
30_showcase_all_operators: SELECT o.orderId, p.name, p.category, o.status FROM ecommerce_orders o JOIN ecommerce_products p ON o.productId = p.id WHERE o.status IN ('delivered', 'shipped') AND p.category NOT IN ('Stationery') AND p.price > 20 AND p.name LIKE '%e%' AND o.deliveryDate IS NOT NULL ORDER BY p.price DESC LIMIT 20
